value.description: In an interview with the LA Times, Suits creator Aaron Korsch credited the show’s renewed success in part to Markle’s role in the royal family. “ [The show] has an inherent optimism to it, and I think that’s a real part of what people respond to,” Korsh said.

value.name: Prince Harry and Meghan, Duchess of Sussex are said to be working on a 'bunch' of fresh projects for Netflix
value.description: After the couple were dealt a massive blow by the streaming giant Spotify when their £15 million contract with the firm ended early in June 2023, Prince Harry and Meghan, Duchess of Sussex are said to be working on a “bunch” of fresh projects for Netflix.
